             was indicted <rs id="t18320906-306-off1727" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18320906-306-off1727" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320906-306-off1727" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               for stealing, on the <rs id="t18320906-306-cd1728" type="crimeDate">29th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320906-306-off1727 t18320906-306-cd1728"></join>, at St. Matthew, Bethnal-green, 40 gold rings, value 10l., the goat of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18320906-306-victim2528" type="victimName">
                           Dickenson 
                           Sowerby
                        <interp inst="t18320906-306-victim2528" type="surname" value="Sowerby"></interp>
